ru.jango.j0loader.queue

Class SingleURIQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.jango.j0loader.queue.DefaultQueue
      • ru.jango.j0loader.queue.SingleURIQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Request>, Queue

    public class SingleURIQueue
extends DefaultQueue
    Special queue for ImageLoader. Basically this loader doesn't need requests' Request.params - it needs only URI, so we can uniquely identify a queue element by it's uri, not combination of uri-params.

    That queue checks URI inside a Request before adding it, so it contains requests with unique URIs.
